---
/**
 * About Section Component
 * Premium, calm layout with center image and left/right content blocks
 * Designed for smooth GSAP scroll-triggered animations
 */
---

<section class="about-section relative bg-ivory py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8">
    
    <!-- Desktop: 3-column grid, Mobile: stacked -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 sm:gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      
      <!-- Left Content Block -->
      <div class="about-left scroll-animate fade-in-left lg:text-right space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
        <div class="inline-block">
          <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-saffron font-medium">
            About Us
          </span>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-tight text-charcoal">
          Education Rooted in Indian Philosophy
        </h2>
        
        <p class="text-ash text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md lg:ml-auto">
          We believe that art is not just performanceâ€”it is a discipline that shapes character, 
          cultivates grace, and connects us to our heritage.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Center Visual -->
      <div class="about-center scroll-animate scale-in flex justify-center lg:order-none order-first lg:order-none">
        <div class="relative">
          <img 
            src="/images/nataraj.png" 
            alt="Indian classical dance representation" 
            class="w-48 sm:w-56 md:w-64 lg:w-80 xl:w-[340px] h-auto object-contain"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Content Block -->
      <div class="about-right scroll-animate fade-in-right space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
        <p class="text-ash text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md">
          Through classical Indian dance, music, and cultural studies, we nurture students 
          who carry forward traditions with authenticity, respect, and purpose.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-ash/70 italic">
          Where tradition meets discipline, and art becomes a way of life.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Ensure smooth transitions */
  .about-left,
  .about-center,
  .about-right {
    will-change: opacity, transform;
  }

  /* Respect reduced motion preferences */
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .about-left,
    .about-center,
    .about-right,
    .scroll-animate {
      opacity: 1 !important;
      transform: none !important;
      animation: none !important;
    }
    
    .scroll-animate.revealed {
      opacity: 1 !important;
    }
  }
</style>
